Watchlist

Where to Watch

Kevin Spacey stars as a homeless man who claims to be a visitor from another planet in this wondrous fable about faith and miracles. He's committed to a mental hospital, where he is treated by a psychiatrist (Jeff Bridges) who's intrigued by his tales and his intelligence. Soon his outlandish story begins to seem plausible. Mary McCormack, Alfre Woodard, David Patrick Kelly.
